name: RARA JONGGRANG
description: Rara Jonggrang is a legend or popular folklore originating from the Special Region of Yogyakarta and also developing in Central Java, Indonesia. This story tells of a prince's love for a princess which ends with the princess being cursed due to a trick he did. This tale also explains the legend of the formation of Sewu Temple, Prambanan Temple, Ratu Baka Palace.
